text: Jérémy Rencurel (born 13 April 1995) is a French BMX rider. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the men's BMX race, in which he was eliminated in the quarterfinals. ==References== == External links == * * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:French male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of France Category:Cyclists at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:BMX riders
